ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether the asserted set of linkages are considered to be "in effect".

ivardefs.name: author
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the user or organization responsible for asserting the linkages and who establishes the context for evaluating the nature of each linkage.

ivardefs.name: item_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies one of the records that is considered to refer to the same real-world occurrence as well as how the items hould be evaluated within the collection of linked items.
